about us
setting:
warm & inviting, southern charm, dine in or alfresco at our outdoor café tables overlooking central park
service:
accommodating & friendly
menu:
classic american cuisine with southern influences
must haves:
homemade lemon raspberry pancakes, brioche french toast, truffle fried eggs, prosecco white peach bellinis, cheese grits, heirloom tomato b.l.t. (seasonal), slice of our homemade layer cakes, to name a few…
also featuring:
burgers, salads, sandwiches, homemade soups, pastries, craft beers, wine & brunch cocktails
.
